Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.scada.ae.Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Event>, java.io.Serializable
    A class holding the AE event information

    Keys and values of the events attributes must not be null. If null is inserted it will simply be ignored.
